                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <video class="animate" playsinline autoplay loop muted>
                        <source src="temp.mp4" type="video/mp4">
                        Your browser does not support the video tag.
                    </video>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="carousel-item">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h3 class="animate">Fan Club Web App with ASP.NET</h3>
                    <p class="animate"><strong>Technology Used:</strong> ASP.NET Core, C#</p>
                    <p class="animate">Designed and developed a dynamic Fan Club Web App, featuring user management and subscription functionality, showcasing expertise in ASP.NET Core and Entity Framework.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <video class="animate" playsinline autoplay loop muted>
                        <source src="fanclub.mp4" type="video/mp4">
                        Your browser does not support the video tag.
                    </video>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="carousel-item">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h3 class="animate">Snake Game Using JavaFX</h3>
                    <p class="animate"><strong>Technology Used:</strong> Java, JavaFX</p>
